{"tid":1245603,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"《蘋果》徵求警察濫權片段 還原反送中衝突真相","createTime":"2019-06-20T11:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T12:28:39.000Z","uid":1174,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"37881e4a1661b50e66534ad079858264123f3c06","tid":1245603,"uid":1174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T11:15:50.000Z","msg":"150枚催淚彈，20發布袋彈，數發橡膠子彈&hellip;&hellip;6月12日數以萬計市民齊集政府總部外，要求撤回送中惡法，最終演變成警民衝突，大批警員手持槍械，不停向手無寸鐵的示威者射擊，和平集會轉瞬間成為烽火連天的戰地，有人頭部中槍，有人倒地不起，有人更險遭被逼向前的人潮踩死。<br />\n<br />\n現場記者人力有限，無法覆蓋每一寸地方，但當日真相亟需揭露。《蘋果》現在向全港讀者徵求6月12日拍攝的任何警察濫權影片，或是提供當日親身被暴力及無理對待經歷，重新還原衝突真相；如有其他涉及反送中的警察濫權片段亦請不吝提供。請將影片原檔發送至以下電郵地址，並附上拍攝時間及位置，《蘋果》將有專人處理及跟進，內容絕對保密。<br />\n<br />\n電郵： investigation@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n電郵： investigation@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n電郵： investigation@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190620/59739333\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190620%2F59739333&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=17e0b75f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190620%2F59739333&h=d4213230\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190620/59739333</a>"},{"pid":"147c8cc199b4c64720261503f581fcad258e83b2","tid":1245603,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T11:16:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"019b1dd168014190d143f8e52bc09fdeb15be88a","tid":1245603,"uid":1174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T11:18:12.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"b42552ab5a5c632db846bb701e5daf09ec95b88f","tid":1245603,"uid":77740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T11:18:44.000Z","msg":"推!!"},{"pid":"e8c2ee71a6c683fad6b7713828e6b9248a370b7a","tid":1245603,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"